<div id="header">
  <div id="logo2">
    <h1><%= link_to "Mikl",new_user_searched_keyword_path(current_user) %><%= link_to ".Me",user_path(current_user) %></h1>
    <div>
      <p>
        <%= link_to_unless_current "搜索链接",new_user_searched_keyword_path(current_user) %>
        <%= link_to_unless_current "搜索人们呓语什么",new_user_searched_content_path(current_user) %>
      </p>
      <%= text_field 'link_url_resource','keywords' %>
      <div class="auto_complete" id="link_url_resource_keywords_auto_complete">
      </div>
      <%= auto_complete_field :link_url_resource_keywords,:url => {:action => 'auto_complete_for_link_url_resource_keywords'},:frequency => 0.1,:after_update_element =>
        "function(element,value){" + remote_function(:url => {:action => :create},:with=>"'keywords='+element.value") + "}"%>
      <div><%= link_to "新增一个搜索链接结果",new_user_link_url_resource_path(current_user),:popup => true%></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="main">
  <div id="more">最近被创建的关键字：
    <% for keyword in @all_keywords %>
      <span><%= link_to "#{keyword}","/keyword_pages/#{KeywordPage.find_by_keyword(keyword).id}",:popup => true,:class => "keywords" %>
      </span>
    <% end %>
    <p>
      <%= link_to_remote "更多>>>",:url => {:action => :about_all_keywords } %>
    </p>
  <p>当您幸运的发现没有出现自动提示的关键字时，就意味着您自己可以任意编辑该关键字的内容，从而被别人看见。 </p>
</div>
  <div id="hide">
  </div>
<%= render :partial => "shared/footer" %>
</div>